---
title: Quick Cheesy Buffalo & Bacon Ciabatta Melt with Corn & Cucumber Salad
description: Our easy ciabatta and bacon melt gives a traditional pizza some fierce competition. We’ve topped crispy ciabatta with a smokey BBQ sauce and bursting corn kernels for extra flavour. Finished with gooey Cheddar cheese and ready in just 20 minutes, this dinner won’t be hanging around for long.
